  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat and render the lardons until crispy.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin seeds, coriander powder, and cayenne pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the kidney beans, salt, and water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 15 minutes.",
    "Add the broken spaghetti and cook until al dente.",
    "Stir in the rendered lardons and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro if desired."
